com.ibm.di.loader

Class TDIJarsLocator

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.ibm.di.loader.TDIJarsLocator

  • public class TDIJarsLocator
extends java.lang.Object
    This class is responsible for locating TDI Jars URLs. Jars are grouped in four categories:

    1. Third Party Jars
    2. Components Jars
    3. Patch Jars
    4. Custom Jars

    Since:
    7.1
